short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: YouTube will automatically shut down if it exceeds the specified time. Don't waste your time anymore.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Save time by reading YouTube viewing time.
